Variable
----------------
$txt = "Hello world!";
$x = 5;
$y = 10.5;

Display output
---------------------
echo "Hello world";
$x = 5;
echo $x;
echo "<h2>" . $x . "</h2>";

Data Types
--------------------
$x = "Hello world!"; //String
$x = 5985;  //integer
$x = 10.365;  //Float
$x = null;
$x = true;  //Boolean
$cars = array(); //Blank Array
$cars = array("Volvo","BMW","Toyota");  //Array
echo $cars[0];
$cars[0] = "Volvo";
$age = array("Peter"=>"35", "Ben"=>"37", "Joe"=>"43");
$str = explode(" ",$x) //String to Array
$y = implode(" ",$x); //Array to String

Multidimensional Arrays:
$cars = array (
  array("Volvo",22,18),
  array("BMW",15,13),
  array("Saab",5,2),
  array("Land Rover",17,15)
);
sort($cars);   //Assending Order (A-Z, 0-9)
rsort($cars); //Dessending Order (Z-A, 9-0)
asort($age); //Ascending Order
ksort($age); //Ascending Order, According to Key
arsort($age); //Descending Order, According to Value
krsort($age); //Descending Order, According to Key

$cars = array(); //Blank Array

Object:

 <?php
class Car {
  public $color;
  public $model;
  public function __construct($color, $model) {
    $this->color = $color;
    $this->model = $model;
  }
  public function message() {
    return "My car is a " . $this->color . " " . $this->model . "!";
  }
}

$myCar = new Car("black", "Volvo");
echo $myCar -> message();
echo "<br>";
$myCar = new Car("red", "Toyota");
echo $myCar -> message();
?> 

